headline: Packaging M&A may not rise until next year, analysts say
summary: Deal volume has been somewhat similar in 2025 as in 2024. Tariff uncertainty could dampen growth in the months to come, analysts note.

headline: International Paper (IP) Completes Sale of Five European Plants to PALM Group
summary: International Paper Company (NYSE:IP) is one of the top 10 materials stocks to buy according to analysts. On July 1, the company finalized the sale of five European corrugated packaging plants to PALM Group.
